						<summary>

						<p>On the south wall of the Siddhēśvara temple. 1100 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the 24th Chālukya-Vikrama year, Pramādi, Phālguṇa ba. 5, Sunday. The details correspond to 1100 A.D., March 2, the weekday being Friday.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land by Prasannarāsi-paṇḍita, the <hi rend="italic">āchārya</hi> of the Siddhēśvara temple, to the tank called <hi rend="italic">Bāchiseṭṭiya-keṟe.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
